ABOUT
electron is a free and open-source kernel, which is also unlicensed. 
Run build.sh to build the latest kernel, after making tweaks.
The main kenel is in source/kernel.c and the boot file is in source/boot.asm. 
# CORE-UTILScore-utils is a set of utilities for the electron kernel. By default, it includes the following commands. 
A - about info
S - shutdown electron
C - clear screen

